Counseling & Psychological Services
The mission of Counseling & Psychological Services (CAPS) is to enhance the psychological well-being of the entire campus community and thereby facilitate the retention and successful educational experience of students, faculty, and staff.
View mission statement
for full description.
*** Please note that we have moved to a new building, the Gator Student Health Center (across from the Mashouf Wellness Center) as of Tuesday, April 1. Please come visit us along with our campus partners, Student Health Services and Health Promotion & Wellness.
All appointments are in the new Gator Student Health Center location.
